<scopecontent encodinganalog="520" id="a3">
<head>Scope and Content</head>
<p>The collection includes drafts and manuscripts of literary materials, correspondence, photographs and publications pertaining to Bertolette's literary and editorial/publishing career. The collection also contains materials concerning his tenure as a student including his years at the <corpname>University of Connecticut</corpname>.</p>
</scopecontent>
